Design vending machine:

Which have given properties:
0. Display the list of items, list of money machine takes.
0.1. Option to select the item then putting money onto it.
1. Accepts money in form of 5, 10, 20, 50, 100rs.
2. Products having amounts like Coke(25), Pepsi(35), Soda(45), Chips(10), Snacks(5)
3. Giving the selected item and returning the change if there.
if money is less warn and request for more money.

4.On cancel returning the money and not giving any thing.